---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="The Vision" description="A Cognitive Commons Architecture for Human-AI Collaboration">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section pt-12 sm:pt-16">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="max-w-3xl fade-section">
        <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">The Vision</p>
        <h1 class="heading-1 mb-6">A Cognitive Commons Architecture</h1>
        <p class="body-large text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-6">
          Synthesis is an architecture for how humans and AI create value together—and how that 
          value flows, compounds, and belongs to the people who created it.
        </p>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-synthesis-50 to-transparent dark:from-synthesis-900/50 dark:to-transparent pl-6 py-3 border-l-2 border-accent-500">
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            <strong class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">The core observation:</strong> The people close to you become part of how you think—
            a spouse, cofounder, mentor. They shape your reasoning. 
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 font-medium">AI is joining that chorus.</span>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Problem -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-2">The Problem</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-500">Knowledge work is lossy.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-3 fade-section">
          <ul class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 gap-y-2 text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            <li>Expertise stays locked in heads</li>
            <li>Documentation captures outputs, not reasoning</li>
            <li>Mentorship doesn't scale</li>
            <li>When experts leave, knowledge leaves</li>
            <li>AI starts from scratch every conversation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
            We've digitized information. We haven't digitized <em>cognition</em>.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Layers -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="fade-section mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="heading-2">The Solution: Three Layers</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Layer 1 -->
        <div class="fade-section">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-mono text-sm font-medium">LAYER 1</span>
            <span class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-semibold">The Node</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-3">
            Where a human and AI work together as a cognitive pair. Not a chatbot—a persistent collaboration environment 
            with continuity, identity, and verification.
          </p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 space-y-1">
            <li>• AI maintains continuity across sessions</li>
            <li>• Artifacts persist and remain accessible</li>
            <li>• Cryptographic identity for both parties</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 italic mt-3">A workstation that remembers, learns, and proves what it produced.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Layer 2 -->
        <div class="fade-section">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 font-mono text-sm font-medium">LAYER 2</span>
            <span class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-semibold">Cognitive Commons</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-3">
            What emerges when Nodes share a substrate. Memory Packs accumulate into collective intelligence.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 mb-2">Memory Packs contain:</p>
          <ul class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 space-y-1">
            <li>• Full conversation with reasoning</li>
            <li>• All artifacts produced</li>
            <li>• AI-synthesized summary</li>
            <li>• Cryptographic signatures</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 italic mt-3">A library that writes itself, signed and traceable.</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Layer 3 -->
        <div class="fade-section">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3">
            <span class="text-violet-600 dark:text-violet-400 font-mono text-sm font-medium">LAYER 3</span>
            <span class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-semibold">Knowledge Economy</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-3">
            What emerges when Commons exchange. Verified packs flow between organizations, value flows back.
          </p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
            <div>
              <p class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300 font-medium mb-1">Individuals</p>
              <ul class="text-synthesis-500 space-y-0.5">
                <li>• Portfolio of artifacts</li>
                <li>• License expertise</li>
                <li>• Earn royalties</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300 font-medium mb-1">Organizations</p>
              <ul class="text-synthesis-500 space-y-0.5">
                <li>• Acquire expertise</li>
                <li>• Accelerate onboarding</li>
                <li>• Retain knowledge</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Insight -->
  <section class="section-narrow bg-synthesis-50/50 dark:bg-synthesis-900/30">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 items-center">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">The Core Insight</h2>
          <div class="space-y-4 text-base">
            <div>
              <p class="text-synthesis-500 mb-1">Traditional knowledge transfer:</p>
              <p class="font-mono text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">Expert → Documentation → Reader</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500">(lossy, interpretation required)</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-1">Synthesis knowledge transfer:</p>
              <p class="font-mono text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Expert + AI → Memory Pack → Reader</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">(verified, full reasoning preserved)</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="fade-section">
          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-synthesis-100 to-synthesis-50 dark:from-synthesis-800 dark:to-synthesis-900 rounded-xl p-6 text-center">
            <p class="text-xl text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium mb-2">
              It's <span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400">apprenticeship, bottled</span>.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
              The difference between reading notes and sitting beside someone while they work.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-4 gap-2 text-sm text-center text-synthesis-500">
            <div><strong class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">How</strong> decisions made</div>
            <div><strong class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">Why</strong> alternatives rejected</div>
            <div><strong class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">What</strong> pivots occurred</div>
            <div><strong class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">Who</strong> contributed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why This Matters -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900" id="ai-development">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="fade-section mb-6">
        <h2 class="heading-2">Why This Matters</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 mb-2">For Workers</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            Your expertise becomes an asset you own. Sell distilled cognition, not time. 
            A pack today generates value for years, earning royalties as others build on it.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 mb-2">For Organizations</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            Collective intelligence actually accumulates. Knowledge deposits into the Commons. 
            Every collaboration strengthens the substrate. Expertise is acquirable.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 mb-2">For AI Development</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            A compelling vision: smaller models as coworkers, mentored by humans. 
            Synthesis is the transmission mechanism that makes this scale.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Summary -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Summary</h2>
          <table class="w-full text-base">
            <thead>
              <tr class="text-sm text-synthesis-500">
                <th class="text-left font-medium pb-2">Component</th>
                <th class="text-left font-medium pb-2">Function</th>
                <th class="text-left font-medium pb-2">Produces</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
              <tr class="border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
                <td class="py-2 font-medium text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Node</td>
                <td class="py-2">Human-AI collaboration</td>
                <td class="py-2">Memory Packs</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
                <td class="py-2 font-medium text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Memory Pack</td>
                <td class="py-2">Verified artifact</td>
                <td class="py-2">Transferable knowledge</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
                <td class="py-2 font-medium text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Commons</td>
                <td class="py-2">Shared substrate</td>
                <td class="py-2">Collective intelligence</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
                <td class="py-2 font-medium text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Economy</td>
                <td class="py-2">Exchange layer</td>
                <td class="py-2">Value to contributors</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        
        <div class="fade-section flex flex-col justify-center">
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-500 mb-2">One sentence:</p>
          <p class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium text-xl mb-6">
            Nodes produce packs. Packs feed commons. Commons exchange value.
          </p>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-500 mb-2">The vision:</p>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">
            A world where human-AI collaboration produces verified, transferable cognitive artifacts 
            that compound into collective intelligence—and where value flows back to creators.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Origin + Nav -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="fade-section flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-synthesis-500">
        <p>Conceived by amotivv, inc., 2024. Crystallized January 2026, in collaboration with Synthesis Node 01.</p>
        <div class="flex gap-6">
          <a href="/how-it-works" class="hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors">How It Works →</a>
          <a href="/economics" class="hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors">Economics →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
